VOTABLE.DESCRIPTION: VizieR Astronomical Server vizier.u-strasbg.fr Date: 2020-10-22T15:57:54 [V1.99+ (14-Oct-2013)] Explanations and Statistics of UCDs: See LINK below In case of problem, please report to: cds-question@unistra.fr In this version, NULL integer columns are written as an empty string , explicitely possible from VOTable-1.3

FIELD.name: Source
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Unique source identifier (unique within a particular Data Release) (source_id) (G2)

FIELD.name: pmRA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Proper motion in right ascension direction (pmRA*cosDE) (pmra) (3)

FIELD.name: e_pmRA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Standard error of proper motion in right ascension direction (pmra_error)

FIELD.name: e_pmDE
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Standard error of proper motion in declination direction (pmdec_error)

FIELD.name: e_Gmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Standard error of G-band mean magnitude (Vega) (added by CDS) (phot_g_mean_mag_error) (37)

FIELD.name: FBP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Mean flux in the integrated BP band (phot_bp_mean_flux)

FIELD.name: e_FBP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Error on the integrated BP mean flux (phot_bp_mean_flux_error) (25)

FIELD.name: e_BPmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Standard error of BP mean magnitude (Vega) (added by CDS) (phot_bp_mean_mag_error) (37)

FIELD.name: FRP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Mean flux in the integrated RP band (phot_rp_mean_flux)

FIELD.name: e_FRP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Error on the integrated RP mean flux (phot_rp_mean_flux_error) (28)

FIELD.name: e_RPmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Standard error of RP mean magnitude (Vega) (added by CDS) (phot_rp_mean_mag_error) (37)

FIELD.name: RV
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Spectroscopic radial velocity in the solar barycentric reference frame (radial_velocity)

FIELD.name: AG
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Estimate of extinction in the G band from Apsis-Priam (a_g_val)

FIELD.name: E(BP-RP)
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Estimate of redenning E(BP-RP) from Apsis-Priam (e_bp_min_rp_val)
